headline: Patricia Gabriel Jumps to PVH From Capri to Lead Supply Chain, Operations
summary: With more than 25 years' experience making consumer companies tick, Gabriel will become chief supply chain officer and global head of operations.

headline: PVH Corp. Names Chief Supply Chain Officer and Global Head of Operations
summary: NEW YORK, October 08, 2025--PVH Corp. (NYSE:PVH) announces the appointment of Patricia Gabriel as Chief Supply Chain Officer and Global Head of Operations.
